## 2. New Clean Architecture Structure

We will refactor and isolate the Auth Module under `backend/src/modules/auth/` using a 4-layered structure:

```text
backend/src/modules/auth/
├── domain/                               # 1. Domain Layer (Pure Enterprise Rules)
│   ├── entities/
│   │   ├── User.js                       # User Business Entity
│   │   └── Worker.js                     # Worker Business Entity
│   └── value-objects/
│       └── MobileNumber.js               # Enforces valid 10-digit mobile rule
├── application/                          # 2. Application Layer (Use Cases & Ports)
│   ├── use-cases/
│   │   ├── SendOtpUseCase.js             # Logic to generate OTP and dispatch SMS
│   │   ├── VerifyOtpUseCase.js           # Verifies OTP and generates JWT session token
│   │   └── RegisterWorkerUseCase.js      # Onboards new Sarthi workers with coordinates
│   └── ports/                            # Ports for outbound drivers (dependency inversion)
│       ├── SmsPort.js                    # Interface for SMS clients
│       └── UserRepositoryPort.js         # Interface for User database queries
├── interfaces/                           # 3. Interface Adapters Layer (Express Controllers)
│   ├── controllers/
│   │   └── AuthController.js             # Receives Express requests, delegates, and returns standard JSON
│   └── routes/
│       └── authRoutes.js                 # HTTP routing declarations
└── infrastructure/                       # 4. Infrastructure Layer (Frameworks & Drivers)
    ├── database/
    │   ├── MongooseUserRepository.js     # Implements UserRepositoryPort using Mongoose User Schema
    │   └── MongooseWorkerRepository.js   # Implements Worker database lookup logic
    ├── services/
    │   ├── Msg91SmsService.js            # MSG91 gateway client implementing SmsPort
    │   └── JwtTokenService.js            # JWT token signer
    └── persistence/
        └── schemas/                      # Database Mongoose Schemas
            ├── UserSchema.js             # Moved from backend/src/models/User.js
            └── WorkerSchema.js           # Moved from backend/src/models/Worker.js
```

